      "containerId": "6XodvZ5FnxDAT41lYGlN_",
      "originalText": "We're using `pandoc` utility tool for generating the md -> Pdf, Word, Txt\n\nuse pandoc + MiKTeX to generate the beautiful exports like latex overleaf pdf export\nrest docx and plain text are eaisly handled by the padoc itself",
